{"article_id":"vHJLsFFAEutw1mFG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"is a nonprofit newsroom","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"that investigates abuses of power .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Sign up","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"to receive our biggest stories","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"as soon as they ' re published .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"It has become a familiar pattern :","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"President Donald Trump says something","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that doesn ' t line up with the facts","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"held by scientists and other experts at government agencies .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Then ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"instead of pushing back ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"federal officials scramble to reconcile the fiction with their own public statements .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"It happened in March ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"when Trump pushed his opinion","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that antimalarial drugs could treat COVID-19 .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention issued an unusual directive","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that lent credence to the president ' s perspective :","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"\" Although optimal dosing and duration of hydroxychloroquine for treatment of COVID-19 are unknown ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"some U.S. clinicians have reported anecdotally \" on specific dosages","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"that the CDC then lists .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"The CDC ' s language","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"- which the agency later retracted -","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"shocked experts ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"the drug needed to be treated with caution .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"The CDC told Reuters","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"the agency had prepared the guidance at the behest of the White House .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Perhaps the best known example of an agency","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"twisting itself into a pretzel","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"stems from \" Sharpiegate. \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"After the National Weather Service ' s Birmingham , Alabama , office contradicted Trump ' s Sharpie fable","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"that Hurricane Dorian threatened the state ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"the agency","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"overseeing the office","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"put out a statement","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"backing the president over the scientists .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Emails","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"obtained by BuzzFeed and The Washington Post","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"showed just how the episode roiled the agency .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"\" You have no idea","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"how hard I ' m fighting to keep politics out of science , \"","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"one official wrote .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Another email simply had one word :","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"\" HELP ! ! ! \"","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"On the same day last week , two separate agencies cut through the White House influence with their own factual conclusions .","depth":3},{"id":45,"text":"Get Our Top Investigations","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Subscribe to the Big Story newsletter .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"The Food and Drug Administration announced last Monday","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that it was revoking emergency approval of the malaria drugs ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that the dosing regimens","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"promoted","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"are \" unlikely to produce an antiviral effect \"","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and that their risks","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"- which include potentially fatal cardiac side effects -","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"outweigh the possible benefits .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Also that day , an independent panel","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"investigating Sharpiegate on behalf of the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"found","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that top officials","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"- including acting chief Neil Jacobs -","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"violated the policy","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that forbids political interference with NOAA ' s scientific findings .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Meanwhile , Trump nominated Jacobs to permanently lead the agency in December .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"catalogued other instances","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"in which government entities have changed language","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"or made other moves","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"buttressing the White House ' s unsupported assertions .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"The morning after Trump ' s son-in-law Jared Kushner asserted","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that the national stockpile is \" our stockpile \" and not for states ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"the government changed the wording on the stockpile ' s website .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Before Kushner ' s comments , it said","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"the \" stockpile ensures","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"that the right medicines and supplies get to those","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"who need them most . \"","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"That became :","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"The stockpile ' s \" role is to supplement state and local supplies , \"","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"and \" many states have products","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"stockpiled , as well . \"","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"A screenshot of the Strategic National Stockpile ' s website after Jared Kushner ' s comment , above , and before his comment .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"A government spokesman said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"the update had been in the works for a week before Kushner ' s comments .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"The spokesperson did not allow their name to be used .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"In another instance ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"after Trump warned in a tweet of \" unknown Middle Easterners \"","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"crossing the border from Mexico","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"- a \" National Emergy","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"[ sic ] \" -","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"the Department of Homeland Security released figures","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"to support the claim .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Upon inspection , it became clear the figures did nothing of the sort .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"A few days later , the president backed off his claim","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"of suspicious Middle Easterners","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"crossing the border .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" There ' s no proof of anything , \"","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"\" but there could very well be . \"","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Agencies ' attempts","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"to bolster the White House","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"haven ' t always borne fruit .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"In late 2018 , Trump again warned about dangers at the Mexican border .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" Women are tied up ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"they ' re bound ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"duct tape put around their faces , around their mouths ,","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"in many cases they can ' t even breathe , \"","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"Trump said .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"\" They ' re put in the backs of cars or vans or trucks . \"","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"It wasn ' t at all clear what Trump was referring to ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"but a top Border Patrol official tried to be of assistance .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"He emailed agents","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"asking them to pass along any such evidence .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"( The email was obtained by a Vox reporter , Dara Lind ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"who ' s now at . )","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"And then there was Trump ' s first day in office .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"He publicly complained about what he said","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"were misleading photographs","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"comparing the size of the audience at his inauguration with President Barack Obama ' s ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"and then-White House Spokesman Sean Spicer falsely claimed a record crowd size .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"A combination of photos","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"taken at the National Mall","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"shows the crowds","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"attending the inauguration ceremonies","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"to swear in Trump , left , in 2017 and President Barack Obama in 2009 .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"( Reuters Staff )","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"The Post soon reported","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"the president called the head of the National Park Service","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"to demand","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"it release photos","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that would counter what he saw as the misleading comparisons .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Sarah Huckabee Sanders , the deputy spokesperson , said","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"the call was simply a reflection of a president","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"who is \" so accessible , and constantly in touch . \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"A government investigation later found","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that after the call a National Park Service photographer cropped photos","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to take out empty areas .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"As the report noted ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"\" He selected a number of photos ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"based on his professional judgment ,","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"that concentrated on the area of the national mall","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"where most of the crowd was standing . \"","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"The report noted","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that no one ordered him to do so .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Congress has also gotten involved .","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"Right before the 2018 elections , Trump made unplanned comments","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"that middle-class Americans would be getting a 10 % tax cut .","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"\" We ' ll be putting it in next week , \"","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"Trump said at a campaign rally in Houston .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Nobody in the White House or Capitol Hill had even heard Trump talk about it before .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"Republicans responded","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"by saying","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"they were working on rolling out something","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"- reportedly a nonbinding resolution -","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"\" over the coming weeks , \"","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"as one congressman put it .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":307,"left":158,"right":306,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":155,"right":157,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":2,"right":156,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":197,"right":305,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":196,"right":44,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":196,"left":5,"right":195,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":195,"left":163,"right":194,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":160,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":6,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":9,"right":161,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":10,